{
  "stem": "12402.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There he met a girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't married.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He met a girl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would have gotten married if the war wouldn't broke out, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it so happened, he-- he left her behind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and she as a matter of fact, I found out after the war, she survived the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anken. ?] Her family of [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anken. ?] They were a very prominent family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I found out from [INAUDIBLE] that she survived the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She went to Russia, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's where she survived the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it happened so that after my brother left-- but the influence, where you know the people from the train, train master.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Vencil ?], would be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was a good friend of the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he got him the last ticket out to go to Warsaw to get the-- the visa to go back to United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he was very lucky, but he left everything behind [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was very lucky he got out of-- alive from that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, he came with a friend on the-- on the ship when he came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In May, when they arrived to-- to home, when they arrived home, so his friend remained behind.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was killed by the Nazis after.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He couldn't make it back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he-- he got killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We found out after the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it happened, so 1939, September the 1st, I remember like-- I remember like now it was-- I was-- I went with my friends, you know, out of the city, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From [? way over there, ?] we saw planes over-- over our heads, flying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it looked so funny, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know the war was on.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
